[[# input]]
++++* Attributes:
+++++* @xsltpath

[[# xsltpath]]

**type:** xs:anyURI **default-value:** ../../xml 
+++++* @scratchpath

[[# scratchpath]]This is the path to scratch space where the eigenvector files EVECFV.OUT, EVECSV.OUT and OCCSV.OUT will be written. If the local directory is accessed via a network then scrpath can be set to a directory on

**type:** xs:anyURI **use:** optional 
+++++* @id

[[# id]]The id is a unique identifier in an input set. If the input element is part of an input set the id must be set.

**type:** xs:ID 
+++++* @depends

[[# depends]]the depends attribute can be used to specify a dependence from another simulation in the same input set.

**type:** xs:IDREFS 

