+ <structureoptimization>
[[# structureoptimization]]The structure optimization element requires a groundstate element to be present
++++* Attributes:
+++++* @epsforce

[[# epsforce]]convergence tolerance for the forces during a structural optimisation run

**type:** fortrandouble **default-value:** 5e-5 
+++++* @tau0atm

[[# tau0atm]]the step size to be used for structural optimisationThe position of atom [[$ \alpha $]]is updated on step [[$ m $]]of a structural optimisation run using 
[[math label]] 
 {\bf r}_{\alpha}^{m+1}={\bf
										r}_{\alpha}^m+\tau_{\alpha}^m \left({ \bf
										F}_{\alpha}^m+{ \bf
										F}_{\alpha}^{m-1}\right), 
[[/math]]
where [[$ \tau_{\alpha} $]]is set to {{ tau0atm }}for [[$ m=0 $]], and incremented by the same amount if the atom is moving in the same direction between steps. If the direction changes then [[$ \tau_{\alpha} $]]is reset to {{ tau0atm }}.

**type:** fortrandouble **default-value:** 0.2d0 
+++++* @resume

[[# resume]]Resumption of structural optimisation run using density in {{ STATE.OUT }}but with positions from {{ exciting.in }}.

**type:** xs:boolean **default-value:** false 

