+++++* @mdfqtype

[[# mdfqtype]]treatment of macroscopic dielectric function for [[$ {\bf Q} $]]-point outside of Brillouin zone. A value of 0 uses the full [[$ {\bf Q} $]]and and the [[$ ({\bf 0},{\bf 0}) $]]component of the microscopic dielectric matrix is used. A value of 1 invokes a decomposition [[$ {\bf Q}={\bf q}+{\bf G}_{\bf q} $]]and and the [[$ ({\bf Q}_{\bf q},{\bf Q}_{\bf q}) $]]component of the microscopic dielectric matrix is used.

**type:** xs:integer **default-value:** 0 
+++++* @fxctype

[[# fxctype]]

**type:**  select:

* RPA
* LRCstatic_NLF
* LRCstatic
* LRCdyn_NLF
* LRCdyn
* ALDA
* MB1_NLF
* MB1  **default-value:** RPA 

